## Rules

1. Always use `--json` for structured output parsing.
2. Never use `iotcli setup` (interactive mode). Use only non-interactive commands.
3. Never guess device names. Always query with `iotcli --json list` first.
4. Always check device status before acting — it may be offline.
5. After controlling a device, optionally re-check status to confirm.
